DOCUMENTATION
generating your project as a package
  > usethis::create_package("../myProjectFolderNameHere")
  
This script helps you to generate the Roxygen2 skeleton for all the functions in your code 
  > sinew::makeOxyFile("R/shield_specification_helpers.R")
  
genrate Rd documentation:
  > devtools::document()
  
generate pdf user manual from Rd documentation:
  > devtools::build_manual()
  